Sentencas: Low-temperature operation of reversible solid oxide cells can effectively improve their stable and economical application.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: However, insufficient catalytic activity of the air electrode is the limiting factor for reversible solid oxide cells.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Here, we fabricate a novel Pr0.9Ag0.1B0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+delta nanofibers with enhanced electrocatalytic activities via an electrospinning technique and in-situ exsolution.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The study confirms the advantage of morphology engineering in enlarging the catalytic interface and reactive sites, and the cells with Pr0.9Ag0.1B0.5Sr0.5Co2O5+delta nanofibers air electrode exhibit obviously decreased polarization resistance (0.06 Omega cm(2)), increased electrolysis current density of 0.65 A cm(-2) (50 vol% absolute humidity and 1.5 V), and adequate power density (similar to 0.5 W cm(-2)) at 700 degrees C. Also, the cell exhibits exceptional reversibility and stability during the long-term test.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The enhancement may be assigned to the in-situ exsolution of Ag nanoparticles at Pr(0.9)Ag(0.1)B(0.5)Sr(0.5)Co(2)O(5+delta )surface and better interface combination between the air electrode and electrolyte.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: This work provides an exemplificative study on the favorable nanofibers air electrode for high performance intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells.
Titulo: Smart utilization of in-situ exsolution occurring in Ag doped PrBa0.5Sr0.5CO2O5+δ nanofiber air electrode of intermediate temperature reversible solid oxide cells
